Installation is simple.

!!NOTICE!!
Machines running Cygwin will have to remove all of the symlinks in the binary path prior to running the installer!!!  VERY IMPORTANT!!!

--SOURCE INSTALL--
First: edit the template files to your liking.
Secondly: run the install.pl script.


--BINARY INSTALL--
Install the version appropriate to your machine
following the instructions provided by the distributor of the binary.


If you have any problems, let me know by sending
email to mstemle1024@msn.com

